---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="레퍼런스커피 - RefX" description="AI 기술로 운영되는 프리미엄 커피 브랜드. DALL-E 3 이미지 생성, GPT-4o 컨텐츠 자동화, 실시간 주문 모니터링 시스템.">
  <Header />

  <main>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-coffee-900 to-coffee-700 text-white py-20">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="flex justify-center items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <span class="text-6xl">☕</span>
            <span class="text-4xl">+</span>
            <span class="text-6xl">🤖</span>
          </div>
          <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-purple-600 text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-full mb-4">AI-Powered Coffee Brand</span>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">레퍼런스커피</h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-coffee-200 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            <strong>AI 기술</strong>로 운영되는 프리미엄 커피 브랜드<br>
            DALL-E 3 이미지 생성 • GPT-4o 컨텐츠 자동화 • 실시간 주문 모니터링
          </p>
          <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="https://smartstore.naver.com/refcoffee" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-white text-coffee-900 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors inline-flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path d="M3 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1H4a1 1 0 01-1-1V4zM3 10a1 1 0 011-1h6a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1H4a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6zM14 9a1 1 0 00-1 1v6a1 1 0 001 1h2a1 1 0 001-1v-6a1 1 0 00-1-1h-2z" />
              </svg>
              스마트스토어에서 주문하기
            </a>
            <a href="https://instagram.com/refx.coffee" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="border-2 border-white text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-white hover:text-coffee-900 transition-colors inline-flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="mr-2">📸</span>
              AI 생성 컨텐츠 보기
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Brand Story -->
    <section class="py-16">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">브랜드 스토리</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-600">
              <p>
                레퍼런스커피는 개발자의 일상에서 시작되었습니다.
                코딩과 함께하는 완벽한 커피를 찾는 여정에서 탄생한 프리미엄 브랜드입니다.
              </p>
              <p>
                우리는 커피 한 잔이 단순한 음료가 아니라, 창작과 집중을 위한 필수 요소라고 믿습니다.
                그래서 엄선된 원두와 정교한 로스팅 과정을 통해
                개발자들의 창의성을 극대화할 수 있는 커피를 만들고 있습니다.
              </p>
              <p>
                기술에 대한 완벽함을 추구하는 마음으로 커피에도 타협하지 않는 품질을 구현합니다.
                매일 마시는 커피가 특별한 경험이 되도록 하는 것이 우리의 목표입니다.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-coffee-50 rounded-lg p-8">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-6xl mb-4">📊</div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-coffee-900 mb-4">성장 지표</h3>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg">
                  <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-coffee-900">200+</div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-coffee-700">만족한 고객</div>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg">
                  <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-coffee-900">7배</div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-coffee-700">단기간 성장률</div>
                  <div class="text-xs text-coffee-600">Instagram 153→200+</div>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg">
                  <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-coffee-900">★4.9</div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-coffee-700">스마트스토어 평점</div>
                  <div class="text-xs text-coffee-600">네이버 고객 리뷰</div>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg">
                  <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-coffee-900">24/7</div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-coffee-700">주문 모니터링</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Product Features -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">왜 레퍼런스커피인가요?</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">개발자를 위해 특별히 설계된 프리미엄 커피</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Quality -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 text-center hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-coffee-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">엄선된 원두</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              세계 각지의 최고 품질 원두만을 엄선하여
              일관된 품질과 풍부한 향을 보장합니다.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Roasting -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 text-center hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-coffee-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 18.657A8 8 0 016.343 7.343S7 9 9 10c0-2 .5-5 2.986-7C14 5 16.09 5.777 17.656 7.343A7.975 7.975 0 0120 13a7.975 7.975 0 01-2.343 5.657z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">정교한 로스팅</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              원두별 최적의 로스팅 프로파일을 적용하여
              각 원두의 고유한 특성을 극대화합니다.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Fresh -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 text-center hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-coffee-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">신선한 배송</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              주문 즉시 로스팅하여 최고의 신선도로
              고객에게 전달되는 시스템을 구축했습니다.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Product Line -->
    <section class="py-16">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">제품 라인업</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">다양한 취향과 상황에 맞는 프리미엄 블렌드</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Morning Blend -->
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-100 to-yellow-100 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🌅</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Morning Code Blend</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                아침 첫 커밋을 위한 부드럽고 깔끔한 맛의 블렌드
              </p>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">
                <span class="font-medium">로스팅:</span> 미디엄 라이트<br>
                <span class="font-medium">맛:</span> 과일향, 꽃향, 밝은 산미
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Focus Blend -->
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100 to-indigo-100 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🎯</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Deep Focus Blend</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                깊은 집중이 필요한 코딩 세션을 위한 진한 풍미
              </p>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">
                <span class="font-medium">로스팅:</span> 미디엄 다크<br>
                <span class="font-medium">맛:</span> 초콜릿, 견과류, 묵직한 바디
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Debug Blend -->
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-red-100 to-pink-100 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🐛</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Debug Blend</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                버그 잡기와 야간 작업을 위한 강렬한 에너지
              </p>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">
                <span class="font-medium">로스팅:</span> 다크<br>
                <span class="font-medium">맛:</span> 카라멜, 스모키, 강한 쓴맛
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Decaf Blend -->
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-100 to-teal-100 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🌙</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Late Night Decaf</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                저녁 시간 코드 리뷰를 위한 카페인 없는 깊은 맛
              </p>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">
                <span class="font-medium">로스팅:</span> 미디엄<br>
                <span class="font-medium">맛:</span> 부드러운 단맛, 밸런스
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Cold Brew -->
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-100 to-blue-100 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🧊</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Cold Brew Special</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                더운 여름 코딩을 위한 특별한 콜드브루 블렌드
              </p>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">
                <span class="font-medium">로스팅:</span> 미디엄<br>
                <span class="font-medium">맛:</span> 달콤함, 부드러운 목넘김
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Single Origin -->
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-100 to-orange-100 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🌍</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Single Origin Series</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                매월 다른 지역의 특별한 원두로 만나는 한정판
              </p>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">
                <span class="font-medium">로스팅:</span> 다양<br>
                <span class="font-medium">맛:</span> 지역별 고유 특성
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- AI Technology Integration -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 text-sm font-semibold rounded-full mb-4">AI-Powered Operations</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">AI 기술로 운영되는 스마트 커피 브랜드</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">OpenAI의 최신 AI 기술로 컨텐츠 생성부터 주문 관리까지 자동화</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <!-- AI Content Generation -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 border-2 border-purple-200">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                <span class="text-white text-xl">🎨</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-xs text-purple-600 font-semibold">AI CONTENT</span>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">AI 이미지 & 컨텐츠 자동 생성</h3>
              </div>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                <div>
                  <strong>DALL-E 3</strong> - 한국 배경 사실적 커피 이미지 자동 생성
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                <div>
                  <strong>GPT-4o</strong> - 상황별 동적 프롬프트 및 캡션 자동 작성
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                <div>
                  <strong>Vision API</strong> - 컨텐츠 품질 분석 및 A/B 테스트
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                <div>
                  <strong>K-Culture 트렌드</strong> - K-드라마/K-pop 문화 자동 반영
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-purple-50 rounded-lg">
              <div class="text-sm text-purple-800">
                <strong>330가지</strong> 프롬프트 조합 • 컨텐츠 품질 <strong>88/100</strong> • 이미지-텍스트 일관성 <strong>95%</strong>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Instagram Automation -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 border-2 border-pink-200">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-500 to-purple-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                <span class="text-white text-xl">📸</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-xs text-pink-600 font-semibold">AUTO POSTING</span>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Instagram 마케팅 자동화</h3>
              </div>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-pink-500 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                <div>
                  <strong>상황별 자동 포스팅</strong> - 아침 7:30 / 오후 15:00 / 저녁 19:00
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-pink-500 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                <div>
                  <strong>AI 이미지 생성</strong> - 시간대별 최적화된 커피 이미지
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-pink-500 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                <div>
                  <strong>해시태그 최적화</strong> - 카테고리별 전략적 20개 배분
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-pink-500 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                <div>
                  <strong>요일/공휴일 반영</strong> - 시즈널 컨텐츠 자동 적용
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-pink-50 rounded-lg">
              <div class="text-sm text-pink-800">
                <strong>200+</strong> 팔로워 달성 • 하루 <strong>3회</strong> 자동 포스팅 • <strong>7배</strong> 성장률
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Order Monitoring -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 border-2 border-green-200">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-xs text-green-600 font-semibold">REAL-TIME</span>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">실시간 주문 모니터링</h3>
              </div>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                <div>
                  <strong>Spring Boot + WebFlux</strong> - 반응형 주문 처리 시스템
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                <div>
                  <strong>텔레그램 실시간 알림</strong> - 신규 주문 즉시 알림
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                <div>
                  <strong>멀티플랫폼 통합</strong> - 네이버/카카오쇼핑 통합 관리
                </div>
              </li>
